\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0 A man entered a downtown street car one day last week. The car was full, and he was obliged to hang onto the strap and ride in the midst of a crowd of good-looking girls, most of whom were either \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93would-bes\u8221\'94 or \u8220\'93has-beens.\u8221\'94 The conversation soon started in his direction, and in secret tone, just loud enough for him to hear, they discussed the new arrival.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Hasn\u8217\'92t he the most lovely hair?\u8221\'94 one of them exclaimed in a whisper that was halfway between awestruck and tender.}
